data.description: Incredible opportunity in Cicero! Huge equity upside! Captivating Brick Georgian Residence: Step into a spacious haven exuding warmth with its brick facade and timeless Georgian design. Within, discover ample living and dining spaces ideal for hosting gatherings or unwinding. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, and transportation, this home caters to both comfort and practicality for homeowners or investors seeking immediate equity. Priced at $100K below the After Repair Value (ARV), seize this opportunity for a lucrative investor/landlord or homeowner. This is a must-see. Sold strictly as-is. Easy access to highways for seamless travel to Chicago and Midway Airports. Welcome Home!! Schedule a showing today!
